name: White Jaguar
overview: Created for the Yandex Retro Games Battle 2020. “… Wauckhen, the time has come. You must go the hard way to your destiny, find yourself in your greatness and become one of us. My friend, do not come behind me - I may not lead you. Don't go ahead of me - maybe I won't follow you. Walk alongside, and we will be one ... "
